title: Pioneer Photo Albums OB-12S Sky Blue Storage Box
description: From scrapbooks to supplies, this heavy-duty scrapbooking storage box by Pioneer will protect your valuable hobby necessities. This durable acid free box is ideal for storing paper, photos, drawings, stickers, embellishments, fabric, ribbon, greeting cards, keepsakes and so much more. This storage box comes equipped with a silver identification slot that makes sorting and identifying projects by subject, date or occasion quick and easy.
